<section class="container my-5">
  <h2 class="text-center mb-4">👨‍💻 About This Portfolio</h2>
  <p>
    Welcome to my personal portfolio website — a full-stack project developed with <strong>Node.js</strong> to present my work, skills, and professional profile in a seamless and interactive manner.
  </p>

  <h4 class="mt-4">🚀 Technologies & Tools Used</h4>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Node.js</strong> – The core of the backend, powering the server-side logic and performance.</li>
    <li><strong>Express.js</strong> – A lightweight and powerful web framework used for handling routes, middleware, and server responses.</li>
    <li><strong>EJS (Embedded JavaScript Templates)</strong> – For rendering dynamic content on the frontend with clean and efficient server-side templates.</li>
    <li><strong>EJS-Mate</strong> – To manage layouts and reusable components, making the templating structure more organized and scalable.</li>
    <li><strong>Bootstrap</strong> – Utilized for responsive design and mobile-first UI components, ensuring consistent layout across devices.</li>
    <li><strong>Nodemailer</strong> – Integrated for handling email functionality, enabling users to contact directly via the portfolio.</li>
    <li><strong>CORS</strong> – Configured to allow cross-origin communication safely and securely.</li>
    <li><strong>Dotenv</strong> - Dotenv is a zero-dependency module that loads environment variables from a .env file into process.env. Storing configuration in the environment separate from code is based on The Twelve-Factor App methodology.</li>
    <li><strong>Render</strong> - This application is deployed and running on Render.</li>
    <li><strong>Universe of UI element</strong> – A modern UI component library that adds visually engaging buttons, cards, toggles, and interactive elements to enhance the user experience with clean and creative design.</li>
  </ul>

  <p class="mt-4">
    This portfolio is not just a static presentation—it's a live, server-rendered application that blends functionality and design. Every section, from the navigation to the contact form, is thoughtfully crafted to reflect professional quality and smooth user interaction.
  </p>
